OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey and cloudy start across
OL,6,Fthe region. Cloud will gradually break
OL,7,Fto give some bright spells across the
OL,8,Fsouth, but staying cloudy in the
OL,9,Fnorth. A few spots of light rain or
OL,10,Fdrizzle possible in Cumbria.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with some outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain across northern parts of the
OL,14,Fregion this evening. Low cloud, mist
OL,15,Fand murk moving into the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA grey start, but cloud
OL,18,Fslowly lifting through the day. Some
OL,19,Fwarm brighter spells are likely at
OL,20,Ftimes, particularly int he south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
