OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FTurning increasingly bright over the
OL,7,Fnext few days with some warm sunny
OL,8,Fspell, particularly in the south where
OL,9,Fit will feel warm. Patchy cloud at
OL,10,Ftimes in the north.
